### 3.2 雙軌並行的地圖格式（向下相容代價巨大）

> [!IMPORTANT]
> 這是專案中最嚴重的技術債。新舊兩套地圖格式同時存在，導致所有讀寫地圖的程式碼都必須處理兩種可能性。

**舊格式** (`WaypointPaths` + `Connections`)：
```json
{
  "WaypointPaths": [[100, 50, 1], [120, 50, 9], ...],  // [x, y, actionCode]
  "Connections": [[0, 1, 1], [1, 2, 0], ...]            // [from, to, isTwoWay]
}
```

**新格式** ([Nodes](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#460-502) + `Edges`)：
```json
{
  "Nodes": [{"Id": "n0", "X": 100, "Y": 50, "Type": "Platform"}, ...],
  "Edges": [{"FromNodeId": "n0", "ToNodeId": "n1", "ActionType": "Walk", "Cost": 20.0}, ...]
}
```

**向下相容造成的程式碼膨脹：**

| 檔案 | 行數 | 職責 |
|---|---|---|
| [LegacyMapMigrator.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Services/LegacyMapMigrator.cs) | 241 行 | 舊→新 ([Migrate](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Services/LegacyMapMigrator.cs#13-156)) 和 新→舊 ([ToEditorFormat](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Services/LegacyMapMigrator.cs#177-223)) 雙向轉換 |
| [MapData.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Models/Map/MapData.cs) L11-13, L24-26 | — | `WaypointPaths` 和 `Connections` 欄位標註「向下相容」 |
| [MapEditor.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/UI/MapEditor.cs) [GetCurrentMapData](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/UI/MapEditor.cs#113-396) L113-395 | **280 行** | 編輯器內部仍用舊格式操作，匯出時轉新格式 |
| [PathPlanningTracker.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs) [LoadMap](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#166-220) L166-219 | 53 行 | 載入時呼叫 [Migrate](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Services/LegacyMapMigrator.cs#13-156) 後再建圖 |

### 3.3 重複的動作碼映射（Action Code 散佈多處）

同一套「動作碼 → 動作類型」的映射至少出現在 **4 個地方**：

1. `LegacyMapMigrator.ConvertActionCode` — 數字 → `NavigationActionType`
2. `LegacyMapMigrator.RevertActionCode` — `NavigationActionType` → 數字
3. `MainForm.OnPathTrackingUpdated` L2074-2085 — `NavigationActionType` → `PathActionType`
4. `MapEditor.GetActionName` — 數字 → 顯示名稱

### 3.4 `PathActionType` vs `NavigationActionType` 重複枚舉

```
// NavigationEdge.cs (Domain 層 - 新)
NavigationActionType { Walk, Jump, JumpLeft, JumpRight, JumpDown, Climb, ClimbUp, ClimbDown, Teleport, FlashJump }

// PathPlanningState.cs 使用的 (隱含在程式碼中 - 舊)
PathActionType { Idle, MoveLeft, MoveRight, Jump, LeftJump, RightJump, JumpDown, ClimbUp, ClimbDown }
```

兩套幾乎相同的枚舉，只因命名不同就需要一個 switch 做轉換 (L2074-2085)。

